 Quilldart shook his head. "So thats how it is then. Well Ill get building on 
some toys for us to use. Those magnet bombs will help. I might be able to 
adjust them to magnet to maximals only since we got predacons coming. He 
turned to Hydras I will get working right away." He exited back to the lab 
asking Starstorm to follow him, he did this to Proto1000 also. Hed need the 
extra hands for speedy work. "We will deal with the humanoid later, he cant 
escape that cell."

--part1_12b.18e196b7.2ad9bda9_boundary
